snippet.title: Abe Peters
snippet.description:
This channel is dedicated to studying the bible by using sound principles and technology. My videos will feature principles that respect the authors of the Scriptures and their contexts. I will also show how to study and teach the bible using low and high tech options.

I love reading the great books so I'll probably show how the great books are influenced by the Bible.
